Text: News from IntelRDelivering Intel technology to your inbox Dear Martin Were contacting you because you signed up at Realcom a while ago to receive news about the IntelR PentiumR III processor and IntelR WebOutfitterSM Service This email is to inform you that you will now receive updates on Intels processors and products for the home courtesy of the free IntelR Home Computing Newsletter In the first issue youll hear about the brand new IntelR PentiumR processor a new generation of processor created to take advantage of tomorrows Internet technology In future issues youll learn about our other products yes we do make more than processors that are making the Internet a more interesting place to be like the IntelR Wireless Game Pad the IntelR Pocket PC Camera and the IntelR AnyPointTM Wireless Home Network tdLkABJjintelwirelessseriesindexhtm tdBEABJjintelpccameraindexhtm tdakABJjintelanypointindexhtm Youll also receive general news and information about how our technology is changing your home computing experience Keep an eye on your inbox Youll be receiving your first issue of the Intel Home Computing Newsletter shortly Subscription Info Change your email address for the Home Computing Newsletter hcupdatedyniszWp Choose from HTML or text as your preferred format for receiving the Home Computing Newsletter hcupdatedyniszWp Unsubscribe from this newsletter in one easy step unsubscribedyniszWp For questions or to make comments or suggestions simply reply to this newsletter Legal Information and Privacy Policy c Intel Corporation tdcEABJjintelsitescorporatetradmarxhtm tdLkABJjintelsitescorporateprivacyhtm
